 Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch (IMPLEMENTATION) Predict Dog Breed with the Model¶

Write a function that takes an image path as input and returns the dog breed (Affenpinscher, Afghan_hound, etc) that is predicted by your model.

Similar to the analogous function in Step 5, your function should have three steps:

  1. Extract the bottleneck features corresponding to the chosen CNN model.
  2. Supply the bottleneck features as input to the model to return the predicted vector. Note that the argmax of this prediction vector gives the index of the predicted dog breed.
  3. Use the dog_names array defined in Step 0 of this notebook to return the corresponding breed.

The functions to extract the bottleneck features can be found in extract_bottleneck_features.py, and they have been imported in an earlier code cell. To obtain the bottleneck features corresponding to your chosen CNN architecture, you need to use the function

extract_{network}

where {network}, in the above filename, should be one of VGG19, Resnet50, InceptionV3, or Xception.

In [83]:
### TODO: Write a function that takes a path to an image as input
### and returns the dog breed that is predicted by the model.
from extract_bottleneck_features import *

def Inception_predict_breed(img_path):
    # extract bottleneck features
    bottleneck_feature = extract_InceptionV3(path_to_tensor(img_path))
    # obtain predicted vector
    predicted_vector = Inception_model.predict(bottleneck_feature)
    # return dog breed that is predicted by the model
    return dog_names[np.argmax(predicted_vector)]

  • if a human is detected in the image, return the resembling dog breed.
  • if neither is detected in the image, provide output that indicates an error.

You are welcome to write your own functions for detecting humans and dogs in images, but feel free to use the face_detector and dog_detector functions developed above. You are required to use your CNN from Step 5 to predict dog breed.

def dog_detector(img_path):
    prediction = ResNet50_predict_labels(img_path)
    return ((prediction <= 268) & (prediction >= 151))  

def face_detector(img_path):
    img = cv2.imread(img_path)
    gray = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)
    faces = face_cascade.detectMultiScale(gray)
    return len(faces) > 0

def Inception_predict_breed(img_path):
    # extract bottleneck features
    bottleneck_feature = extract_InceptionV3(path_to_tensor(img_path))
    # obtain predicted vector
    predicted_vector = Inception_model.predict(bottleneck_feature)
    # return dog breed that is predicted by the model
    return dog_names[np.argmax(predicted_vector)]

def image_detection(img_path):
    
    dog = dog_detector(img_path)
    human = face_detector(img_path)
    
    if dog:
        return('This Dog is a ' + str(Inception_predict_breed(img_path)))
    elif human:
        return('This Person looks like a ' + str(Inception_predict_breed(img_path)))
    else:
        return('Error: Please input a picture of a Dog or a Person ')

In this section, you will take your new algorithm for a spin! What kind of dog does the algorithm think that you look like? If you have a dog, does it predict your dog's breed accurately? If you have a cat, does it mistakenly think that your cat is a dog?

(IMPLEMENTATION) Test Your Algorithm on Sample Images!¶

Test your algorithm at least six images on your computer. Feel free to use any images you like. Use at least two human and two dog images.

Question 6: Is the output better than you expected :) ? Or worse :( ? Provide at least three possible points of improvement for your algorithm.

Answer:

The algorithm was tested on three categories of images, images without dogs or people, images with a dog, and images with a person. The output for the images without people or dogs was as anticipated, the dog_detector function did not detect a dog and the face_detector function did not detect a human face in these images. The results can be shown below, there is an image of a beach that did not get detected as an image with a dog or a person and the output is 'Error: Please input a picture of a Dog or a Person '. The picture of the Praying Mantis also generated the previously stated output.

When the input to the algorithm was a picture of myself, it did the anticipated action of identifying a human face with the face_detector funtion and then it returned what dog breed I look like (Daschund).

The two pictures of my Jack Russell Terrier I input into the function were correctly identified as having a dog in them but the breed was incorrect. I am not surprised that the breed was not correctly identified considering that the accuracy of the dog breed CNN was a little better than 80%. I think that in order to correctly identify the breed of a dog image that is input to the algorithm the Inception_predict_breed algorthim would probably have to be in the high 90% range of accuracy on a test set.

Three ways to improve the algorithm.

1) Add more layers to the pre-trained model

Transfer learning could be used and more experimentation could be done as far as adding layers to the CNN. Adding fully connected layers and convolution layers with more filters may be able to pick up more fine tuned patterns in the image. Recognizing 133 different dog breeds is a very specific task and more filters may be needed.

2) Data augmentation

Data augmentation can also be used to train the CNN with images of dogs that are at various angles and positions in the image. The idea is to achieve rotation and translation invariance, meaning the orientation and position of the dog in the image does not affect the CNNs capability to identify it.

3) Make a model from scratch

It may be the case that making a CNN from scratch would have better results than using transfer learning. Making a CNN from scratch would possibly have fundamental pattern filters that are more specific to identifying dogs instead of various images that the pre-trained model has been trained on.

4) More training data

Identifying 133 dog breeds from pictures is a very specific task that few people can probably achieve with perfect accuracy. If 60,000 training images were used the CNN would probably do a better job. Two dogs that are the same breed can look very different, for example the Jack Russell in the images that I tested is much smaller than the average Jack Russell. This may throw a CNN off unless it has been trained on a wide variety of Jack Russells.
